  "page": "Gareth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The name <b>Gareth</b> is a common first name in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. It can refer to the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_(maester)\" title=\"Gareth (maester)\">Gareth</a>, the author of <i>Red Sands</i> on the Conquest of Dorne.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Clifton\" title=\"Gareth Clifton\">Gareth Clifton</a>, the husband to Lady Jeyne Farman.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_II_Gardener\" title=\"Gareth II Gardener\">Gareth II Gardener</a>, a King of the Reach.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_the_Grey\" title=\"Gareth the Grey\">Gareth the Grey</a>, a supporter of Daemon I Blackfyre during the First Blackfyre Rebellion.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Long\" title=\"Gareth Long\">Gareth Long</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Tyrell\" title=\"Gareth Tyrell\">Gareth Tyrell</a>, the first High Steward of the Reach.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gareth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gared\" title=\"Gared\">Gared</a>, a ranger from the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garrett_Flowers\" title=\"Garrett Flowers\">Garrett Flowers</a>, the bastard son of Garth Tyrell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garrett_Paege\" title=\"Garrett Paege\">Garrett Paege</a>, a squire from House Paege</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garth\" title=\"Garth\">Garth</a>, a disambiguation page for all characters named Garth</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404030148\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 